headline: Cintas Corporation Announces Webcast for Second Quarter Fiscal Year 2025 Results
summary: CINCINNATI, December 05, 2024--Cintas Corporation (Nasdaq: CTAS) today announced that it will release fiscal year 2025 second quarter results on Thursday, December 19, 2024. The Company will conduct a conference call to address the financial results. A live webcast of the call will be available to individual investors and the public beginning at 10:00 a.m., Eastern Time, on Thursday, December 19, 2024.
